FBIS4-38672 "drsov106_s_94007" FBIS-SOV-94-106 Daily Report 31 May 1994 Georgia Parliament Creates Commission To Fight `Mafia' Parliament Creates Commission To Fight `Mafia' NC0106153494 Yerevan SNARK in English 1620 GMT 31 May 94 NC0106153494 Yerevan SNARK English BFN [Text] Tbilisi, 31 May (SNARK) -- Today Georgian Parliament accepted a decision to create a special commission to struggle against the mafia. The decision is the result of the discussion the deputies were taking round the worsening criminal situation existing in Georgia. Irina Sarishvili, one of the leaders of the National-Democratic Party, said at today's session, "no doubt, mafia is heading Georgian state."
